{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841618807,"sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","part":{"id":"prt_d7866e82f001JV2L8Zdx3kYj3O","messageID":"msg_d7865e947001nirgJAB5v6pbh5","sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-697fb7a9e8e34d8e8ffb4d9e718dadf1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md","content":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Proposal\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 WorkloadManager 构建 HTTP 服务框架，作为 agentcube 核心服务器的网络层基础，提供:\n\n1. **RESTful API 基础设施**: 支持 Sandbox、SandboxClaim、Session 等资源的 CRUD 操作\n2. **中间件架构**: 提供请求日志、认证、限流、CORS 等可插拔能力\n3. **生命周期管理**: 优雅启动、信号处理、连接清理\n4. **可观测性**: 健康检查、就绪探针、Prometheus 指标端点\n5. **错误处理**: 统一的错误响应格式与日志记录\n\n## Scope\n\n### In Scope\n\n| Deliverable | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现，包括启动、关闭、配置 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由初始化与路由组管理 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/base.go` | 基础 Handler 接口定义 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health.go` | 健康检查与就绪探针实现 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/logging.go` | 请求日志中间件 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery.go` | Panic 恢复中间件 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/cors.go` | CORS 中间件（可选） |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` | 请求/响应数据结构定义 |\n\n### API Endpoints Framework\n\n```\n/api/v1/\n├── healthz          — 健康检查 (GET)\n├── readyz           — 就绪探针 (GET)\n├── sandboxes        — Sandbox CRUD (待后续 AR 实现)\n├── sandboxclaims    — SandboxClaim CRUD (待后续 AR 实现)\n└── sessions         — Session 管理 (待后续 AR 实现)\n```\n\n### Out of Scope\n\n- 业务 Handler 实现（Sandbox、SandboxClaim、Session）\n- WebSocket 路由与连接管理\n- 认证授权逻辑\n- 具体的限流策略实现\n- 数据库/存储层集成\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Upstream Dependencies\n\n| Dependency | Impact |\n|------------|--------|\n| Go 标准库 `net/http` | 核心依赖 |\n| 可能的第三方路由库（如 chi, gorilla/mux） | 待设计决策，可选 |\n\n### Downstream Consumers\n\n| Consumer | Usage |\n|----------|-------|\n| WorkloadManager 业务逻辑 | 通过 Handler 接口注册业务逻辑 |\n| 监控系统 | 通过 `/metrics` 端点采集指标 |\n| Kubernetes 探针 | 通过 `/healthz`, `/readyz` 检查服务状态 |\n| 客户端应用 | 通过 RESTful API 访问服务 |\n\n### Breaking Change Considerations\n\n- **路由路径变更**: API 路径设计影响所有客户端\n- **错误格式变更**: 统一错误响应格式影响客户端错误处理逻辑\n- **中间件顺序**: 中间件执行顺序可能影响请求处理流程\n\n## Alternatives Considered\n\n### Alternative 1: 使用标准库 net/http\n\n**Approach**: 仅使用 `net/http` 标准库，手动实现路由与中间件。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 无外部依赖；完全控制；性能最优 |\n| Cons | 路由功能有限；需要手动实现中间件链；缺乏社区生态 |\n\n**Decision**: 待评估。对于简单场景可行，但路由分组、路径参数等功能需要额外实现。\n\n### Alternative 2: 使用 gorilla/mux\n\n**Approach**: 使用成熟的 `gorilla/mux` 路由库。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 功能完善；社区活跃；中间件支持好 |\n| Cons | 外部依赖；性能略逊于 chi |\n\n**Decision**: 可选方案。\n\n### Alternative 3: 使用 chi 路由器\n\n**Approach**: 使用轻量级 `chi` 路由器。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 零依赖；性能优秀；兼容 net/http；内置中间件 |\n| Cons | 社区规模小于 gorilla/mux |\n\n**Decision**: 推荐。chi 轻量且符合 Go 惯例。\n\n### Alternative 4: 使用 Gin/Echo 框架\n\n**Approach**: 使用完整 Web 框架（Gin 或 Echo）。\n\n| Aspect | Evaluation |\n|--------|------------|\n| Pros | 功能全面；性能优秀；生态丰富 |\n| Cons | 过度封装；违反 AgentCube 渐进式设计原则 |\n\n**Decision**: 拒绝。AgentCube 倾向于使用标准库 + 轻量级工具，而非重型框架。\n\n## Risks\n\n| Risk | Mitigation |\n|------|------------|\n| 路由库选型错误 | 设计阶段充分评估 chi/gorilla/mux/stdlib，保留切换能力 |\n| 中间件顺序导致 Bug | 明确中间件执行顺序文档，添加集成测试 |\n| 错误响应格式不统一 | 定义 Error 结构体，所有 Handler 使用统一错误返回方法 |\n| 性能瓶颈 | 基准测试关键端点，监控 p99 延迟 |\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n1. **配置**: 使用环境变量或配置文件指定端口、超时等参数\n2. **日志**: 集成 pkg/logging，记录请求 ID、路径、状态码、延迟\n3. **优雅关闭**: 监听 SIGTERM/SIGINT，等待现有连接完成（最长 30s）\n4. **健康检查**: `/healthz` 总是返回 200，`/readyz` 检查依赖服务状态\n5. **中间件模式**: 使用 Go 标准中间件签名 `func(http.Handler) http.Handler`\n\n## References\n\n- Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n- chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n- Kubernetes Healthz Pattern: https://kubernetes.io/docs/tasks/configure-pod-container/configure-liveness-readiness-probes/"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775841618785,"end":1775841618806}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841618809,"sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","part":{"id":"prt_d78663d3c001Ky92wW51rNf6UJ","messageID":"msg_d7865e947001nirgJAB5v6pbh5","sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-c41e7d3966d24dfc96c6c4eeedf28b39","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md","content":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-0 |\n\n## Scope\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，包括:\n- HTTP 服务器配置与生命周期管理\n- 路由设计与中间件架构\n- 请求/响应数据结构定义\n- 健康检查与指标暴露端点\n- 错误处理与日志记录机制\n\n## Out of Scope\n\n- 业务逻辑实现（Sandbox 创建、调度等）\n- WebSocket 连接管理\n- 认证授权实现\n- 具体业务 API 端点实现\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `net/http` 标准库\n- 可能的第三方 HTTP 路由库（待设计确认）\n- 日志库（pkg/logging 或第三方）\n\n## Deliverables\n\n| File | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` | HTTP 服务器核心实现 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go` | 路由配置与中间件 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/` | Handler 接口与基础实现 |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/` | 中间件实现 |\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] HTTP 服务器支持优雅启动和关闭\n- [ ] 路由框架可扩展，支持标准 RESTful API\n- [ ] 中间件链可配置\n- [ ] 健康检查端点可访问\n- [ ] 错误响应格式统一\n- [ ] 通过 `go vet` 和 `golangci-lint`\n\n## References\n\n- Go net/http 文档: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/spec.md","time":{"start":1775841618780,"end":1775841618808}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841618811,"sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","part":{"id":"prt_d7867a9e9001SfVe2TP5qQRpGU","messageID":"msg_d7865e947001nirgJAB5v6pbh5","sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-26fcf7ecafbd4807a16c31e63835721a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","content":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 WorkloadManager 的 HTTP 服务框架，提供 RESTful API 基础设施、中间件架构、生命周期管理。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\n```\ncmd/workload-manager/\n    └── main.go                    — 入口，调用 pkg/workloadmanager\npkg/workloadmanager/\n    ├── server.go                  — HTTPServer 核心实现\n    ├── router.go                  — 路由配置与路由组\n    ├── config.go                  — 配置结构体\n    ├── types.go                   — 公共类型定义\n    ├── handlers/\n    │   ├── handler.go             — Handler 接口\n    │   └── health.go              — 健康检查实现\n    └── middleware/\n        ├── logging.go             — 请求日志中间件\n        ├── recovery.go            — Panic 恢复中间件\n        └── cors.go                — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n### Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `net/http` | 标准库 HTTP 服务器 |\n| `context` | 请求上下文 |\n| `sync` | 并发控制（优雅关闭） |\n| `os/signal` | 信号处理 |\n| `time` | 超时配置 |\n\n### Router Library Selection\n\n**决策**: 使用 `go-chi/chi` v5\n\n| Aspect | Rationale |\n|--------|-----------|\n| 零外部依赖 | 仅依赖 Go 标准库 |\n| 兼容 net/http | 可使用所有标准库中间件 |\n| 路由分组 | 支持路由组与中间件作用域 |\n| 性能 | 足够优秀（参考 benchmark） |\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### server.go\n\n```go\ntype HTTPServer struct {\n    server   *http.Server\n    router   chi.Router\n    config   Config\n    handlers map[string]Handler\n    logger   Logger\n    stopCh   chan struct{}\n}\n\ntype Config struct {\n    Addr              string        // 监听地址，如 \":8080\"\n    ReadTimeout       time.Duration // 读超时\n    WriteTimeout      time.Duration // 写超时\n    IdleTimeout       time.Duration // 空闲连接超时\n    ShutdownTimeout   time.Duration // 优雅关闭超时\n    EnableHealthz     bool          // 是否启用健康检查\n    EnableReadyz      bool          // 是否启用就绪探针\n}\n```\n\n### router.go\n\n```go\ntype Router struct {\n    chi.Router\n}\n\nfunc NewRouter() *Router {\n    r := chi.NewRouter()\n    return &Router{Router: r}\n}\n\nfunc (r *Router) RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler) {\n    for _, h := range handlers {\n        h.Register(r.Router)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### handlers/handler.go\n\n```go\ntype Handler interface {\n    Register(r chi.Router)\n}\n\ntype HandlerFunc func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) error\n\nfunc (hf HandlerFunc) ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    if err := hf(w, r); err != nil {\n        HandleError(w, r, err)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### handlers/health.go\n\n```go\ntype HealthHandler struct {\n    checker HealthChecker\n}\n\ntype HealthChecker interface {\n    IsHealthy() bool\n    IsReady() bool\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) Register(r chi.Router) {\n    r.Get(\"/healthz\", h.healthz)\n    r.Get(\"/readyz\", h.readyz)\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ok\"})\n}\n\nfunc (h *HealthHandler) readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n    if h.checker == nil || !h.checker.IsReady() {\n        w.WriteHeader(http.StatusServiceUnavailable)\n        json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"not ready\"})\n        return\n    }\n    w.WriteHeader(http.StatusOK)\n    json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(map[string]string{\"status\": \"ready\"})\n}\n```\n\n### middleware/logging.go\n\n```go\ntype LoggingMiddleware struct {\n    logger Logger\n}\n\nfunc (m *LoggingMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        start := time.Now()\n        \n        ww := &responseWriterWrapper{ResponseWriter: w}\n        next.ServeHTTP(ww, r)\n        \n        m.logger.Info(\"request\",\n            \"method\", r.Method,\n            \"path\", r.URL.Path,\n            \"status\", ww.status,\n            \"duration\", time.Since(start),\n        )\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### middleware/recovery.go\n\n```go\ntype RecoveryMiddleware struct {\n    logger Logger\n}\n\nfunc (m *RecoveryMiddleware) Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        defer func() {\n            if err := recover(); err != nil {\n                m.logger.Error(\"panic recovered\", \"error\", err, \"path\", r.URL.Path)\n                http.Error(w, \"Internal Server Error\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n            }\n        }()\n        next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### types.go\n\n```go\ntype ErrorResponse struct {\n    Code    string `json:\"code\"`\n    Message string `json:\"message\"`\n    Details any    `json:\"details,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype SuccessResponse struct {\n    Data any `json:\"data\"`\n}\n\nfunc HandleError(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, err error) {\n    // 根据 error 类型映射到 HTTP 状态码\n    // 统一返回 ErrorResponse JSON\n}\n```\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### Health Endpoints\n\n| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|---------|\n| `/healthz` | GET | 健康检查（Kubernetes liveness probe） |\n| `/readyz` | GET | 就绪探针（Kubernetes readiness probe） |\n\n### API Group\n\n| Prefix | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `/api/v1` | 业务 API 路由组（待后续 AR 实现） |\n\n### Middleware Chain\n\n```\nRecovery → Logging → CORS (optional) → Business Handler\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\n| Error Type | HTTP Status | Error Code |\n|------------|-------------|------------|\n| Validation Error | 400 | `VALIDATION_ERROR` |\n| Not Found | 404 | `NOT_FOUND` |\n| Internal Error | 500 | `INTERNAL_ERROR` |\n| Service Unavailable | 503 | `SERVICE_UNAVAILABLE` |\n\n统一错误响应格式:\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n  \"message\": \"Invalid request parameter\",\n  \"details\": {\"field\": \"name\", \"reason\": \"required\"}\n}\n```\n\n## Testing Strategy\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n| Test Category | Coverage |\n|---------------|----------|\n| HTTPServer 启动/关闭 | 测试优雅关闭逻辑 |\n| HealthHandler | 测试 `/healthz` 和 `/readyz` 端点 |\n| Middleware | 测试日志、恢复、CORS 中间件 |\n| 错误处理 | 测试 HandleError 返回正确的 JSON 格式 |\n\n### Integration Tests\n\n| Test | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| 端到端请求 | 启动真实 HTTP 服务器，发送请求并验证响应 |\n| 中间件链 | 验证中间件按预期顺序执行 |\n\n### Test File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  server_test.go\n  router_test.go\n  handlers/health_test.go\n  middleware/logging_test.go\n  middleware/recovery_test.go\n```\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\n  server.go              — HTTPServer 实现\n  router.go              — Router 封装\n  config.go              — Config 结构体\n  types.go               — 公共类型定义\n  handlers/\n    handler.go           — Handler 接口\n    health.go            — HealthHandler 实现\n  middleware/\n    logging.go           — 日志中间件\n    recovery.go          — Panic 恢复中间件\n    cors.go              — CORS 中间件\n```\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- 是否需要 WebSocket 支持？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n- 是否需要限流中间件？（暂不在范围内，待后续 AR）\n- 日志库选型：pkg/logging 还是第三方（如 zap、logrus）？\n- 指标端点 `/metrics` 是否在本 AR 范围内？（建议预留路由，实现待后续 AR）\n\n## References\n\n- chi router: https://github.com/go-chi/chi\n- Go net/http: https://pkg.go.dev/net/http\n- Kubernetes API conventions: https://git.k8s.io/community/contributors/devel/sig-architecture/api-conventions.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/design.md","time":{"start":1775841618790,"end":1775841618810}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775841618814,"sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","part":{"id":"prt_d7868aa93001N77LQWfmi3Y21b","messageID":"msg_d7865e947001nirgJAB5v6pbh5","sessionID":"ses_2879a5db4ffezIf4oMcugo9rIb","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-28a73df2303a49e1ae0d0726bf7cd3b9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-004/tasks.md","content":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Tasks\n\n## Metadata\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 |\n| Module | `pkg/workloadmanager` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | M |\n| Design | [Stage ST-1 pending] |\n\n---\n\n## Task Checklist\n\n### Phase 1: Project Setup\n\n- [ ] **T1.1** Create directory structure `pkg/workloadmanager/`\n  - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/`\n  - [ ] Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/`\n\n- [ ] **T1.2** Add dependency `github.com/go-chi/chi/v5` to `go.mod`\n  - Verify: `go get github.com/go-chi/chi/v5 && go mod tidy`\n\n### Phase 2: Core Type Definitions\n\n- [ ] **T2.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n  - Define `ErrorResponse` struct\n  - Define `SuccessResponse` struct\n  - Define `HandleError` function\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n- [ ] **T2.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/config.go`\n  - Define `Config` struct with fields: `Addr`, `ReadTimeout`, `WriteTimeout`, `IdleTimeout`, `ShutdownTimeout`, `EnableHealthz`, `EnableReadyz`\n  - Define `DefaultConfig()` function\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n### Phase 3: Router Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/router.go`\n  - Import `github.com/go-chi/chi/v5`\n  - Define `Router` struct wrapping `chi.Router`\n  - Implement `NewRouter()` constructor\n  - Implement `RegisterHandlers(handlers ...Handler)` method\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n### Phase 4: Handler Interface & Health Handler\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/handler.go`\n  - Define `Handler` interface with `Register(r chi.Router)` method\n  - Define `HandlerFunc` type and `ServeHTTP` implementation\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/`\n\n- [ ] **T4.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health.go`\n  - Define `HealthChecker` interface with `IsHealthy()` and `IsReady()` methods\n  - Define `HealthHandler` struct with `checker` field\n  - Implement `NewHealthHandler(checker HealthChecker)` constructor\n  - Implement `Register(r chi.Router)` method\n  - Implement `healthz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)` handler\n  - Implement `readyz(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request)` handler\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/`\n\n### Phase 5: Middleware Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/logging.go`\n  - Define `LoggingMiddleware` struct with `logger` field\n  - Implement `NewLoggingMiddleware(logger Logger)` constructor\n  - Implement `Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler` method\n  - Define `responseWriterWrapper` struct to capture status code\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/`\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery.go`\n  - Define `RecoveryMiddleware` struct with `logger` field\n  - Implement `NewRecoveryMiddleware(logger Logger)` constructor\n  - Implement `Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler` method\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/`\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/cors.go`\n  - Define `CORSMiddleware` struct with config fields\n  - Implement `NewCORSMiddleware(...)` constructor\n  - Implement `Wrap(next http.Handler) http.Handler` method\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/`\n\n### Phase 6: Server Implementation\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go`\n  - Define `HTTPServer` struct with fields: `server`, `router`, `config`, `handlers`, `logger`, `stopCh`\n  - Implement `NewHTTPServer(cfg Config, logger Logger) *HTTPServer` constructor\n  - Implement `RegisterHandler(name string, h Handler)` method\n  - Implement `setupRouter()` private method\n  - Implement `setupMiddleware()` private method\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n- [ ] **T6.2** Implement `HTTPServer.Start()` method\n  - Configure `http.Server` with timeouts\n  - Start HTTP server with `ListenAndServe`\n  - Return error channel for async error handling\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n- [ ] **T6.3** Implement `HTTPServer.Stop(ctx context.Context)` method\n  - Call `http.Server.Shutdown(ctx)`\n  - Wait for existing connections to complete\n  - Close `stopCh` to signal shutdown complete\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n- [ ] **T6.4** Implement `HTTPServer.GracefulShutdown()` method\n  - Setup signal handler for SIGTERM and SIGINT\n  - Call `Stop()` on signal\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/`\n\n### Phase 7: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T7.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/types_test.go`\n  - Test `HandleError` returns correct JSON format\n  - Test `SuccessResponse` marshals correctly\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go`\n  - Test `NewHTTPServer` with default config\n  - Test `Start()` and `Stop()` lifecycle\n  - Test graceful shutdown with context timeout\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/router_test.go`\n  - Test `NewRouter()` returns valid router\n  - Test `RegisterHandlers()` registers multiple handlers\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/health_test.go`\n  - Test `healthz` returns 200 with `{\"status\": \"ok\"}`\n  - Test `readyz` returns 200 when `IsReady() == true`\n  - Test `readyz` returns 503 when `IsReady() == false`\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/handlers/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/logging_test.go`\n  - Test logging middleware captures request method, path, status\n  - Test `responseWriterWrapper` captures status code\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.6** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/recovery_test.go`\n  - Test recovery middleware catches panic\n  - Test recovery middleware returns 500 on panic\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/... -v`\n\n- [ ] **T7.7** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/cors_test.go`\n  - Test CORS middleware adds `Access-Control-Allow-Origin` header\n  - Test CORS middleware handles preflight OPTIONS request\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/middleware/... -v`\n\n### Phase 8: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **T8.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_test.go`\n  - Start real HTTP server on random port\n  - Send GET request to `/healthz` and verify response\n  - Send GET request to `/readyz` and verify response\n  - Verify middleware chain executes in correct order\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -tags=integration`\n\n### Phase 9: Validation & Quality\n\n- [ ] **T9.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n  - Fix any issues reported\n\n- [ ] **T9.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n  - Fix any linting issues\n\n- [ ] **T9.3** Verify HTTP server supports graceful shutdown\n  - Send SIGTERM signal to running server\n  - Verify server stops accepting new connections\n  - Verify existing connections complete within timeout\n\n- [ ] **T9.4** Verify health endpoints work with Kubernetes probes\n  - Test `curl http://localhost:8080/healthz`\n  - Test `curl http://localhost:8080/readyz`\n\n### Phase 10: Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T10.1** Add godoc comments to all exported types and functions\n- [ ] **T10.2** Add package-level documentation in `pkg/workloadmanager/doc.go`\n- [ ] **T10.3** Document middleware execution order in `README.md` or design notes\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1.1 → T1.2 → T2.1 → T2.2 → T3.1 → T4.1 → T4.2\n                                            ↓\n                          T5.1 → T5.2 → T5.3\n                                            ↓\n                          T6.1 → T6.2 → T6.3 → T6.4\n                                            ↓\n                          T7.1 → T7.2 → T7.3 → T7.4 → T7.5 → T7.6 → T7.7\n                                            ↓\n                                          T8.1\n                                            ↓\n                          T9.1 → T9.2 → T9.3 → T9.4\n                                            ↓\n                          T10.1 → T10.2 → T10.3\n```\n\n---\n\n## Verification Commands\n\n| Task | Verification Command |\n|------|----------------------|\n| T1.2 | `go mod tidy && go mod verify` |\n| T2.1-T6.4 | `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` |\n| T7.1-T7.7 | `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v` |\n| T8.1 | `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -tags=integration` |\n| T9.1 | `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` |\n| T9.2 | `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` |\n| T9.3 | `kill -SIGTERM <pid>` and observe logs |\n| T9.4 | `curl http://localhost:8080/healthz` |\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] HTTP server starts on configured address\n- [ ] HTTP server supports graceful shutdown\n- [ ] Router framework supports route grouping and middleware\n- [ ] Health check endpoints (`/healthz`, `/readyz`) respond correctly\n- [ ] Middleware chain executes in correct order\n- [ ] Error responses use unified JSON format\n- [ ] Pass `go vet` with zero issues\n- [ ] Pass `golangci-lint` with zero issues\n- [ ] Unit tests pass with >80% coverage\n- [ ] Integration tests pass\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Use `github.com/go-chi/chi/v5` for routing\n- Follow Go standard library conventions for HTTP handlers\n- Graceful shutdown timeout should be configurable (default 30s)\n- Middleware should use standard `func(http.Handler) htt